01:31.520 --> 01:31.920
Nice.

01:31.920 --> 01:34.880
But the school board sent the money back.

01:34.880 --> 01:36.560
They said that if they took it,

01:36.560 --> 01:41.920
students would have to watch pro-LGBTQ videos, which wasn't true.

01:41.920 --> 01:44.480
It Gets Better does focus on helping LGBTQ kids,

01:44.480 --> 01:46.080
but the room would have been open to anyone,

01:46.080 --> 01:48.720
and the grant had no requirements about watching anything.

01:48.720 --> 01:51.200
But the board wouldn't listen.

01:51.200 --> 01:53.920
The board discussed this for longer than they discussed

01:53.920 --> 01:57.920
the literal closure of two entire schools in their district.

01:57.920 --> 01:59.600
And that stunned me.

01:59.600 --> 02:02.480
A school board rejected $10,000 of free money

02:02.480 --> 02:04.960
and talked about something that isn't true for so long.

02:04.960 --> 02:07.040
