40:02.400 --> 40:04.080
is because they're so gosh darn sneaky.

40:04.880 --> 40:08.480
Self-victimization plays a huge role here.

40:08.480 --> 40:09.760
Another reason there's no evidence

40:09.760 --> 40:12.480
