41:15.680 --> 41:19.120
It kind of just means the opposite of how things should be,

41:20.000 --> 41:24.240
and the way they should be is whatever you personally want.

41:25.040 --> 41:27.280
And that's a very effective strategy,

41:27.280 --> 41:29.040
because it allows people who previously

41:29.040 --> 41:32.000
