I like that the worms are never confirmed to be real.

57:35.600 --> 57:38.000
We could read them as hallucinations.

57:39.040 --> 57:42.080
That ambiguity forces us to engage only with the metaphor.

57:42.800 --> 57:44.080
Brainworms might not be real,

57:45.040 --> 57:51.680
but hate is infectious, disgusting, and perverse.

57:51.680 --> 57:53.920
One character is a famous author

57:53.920 --> 57:56.400
who writes books about teenage witches.

57:59.200 --> 58:01.920
There's a scene where she infects someone else,

58:01.920 --> 58:05.760
coming close to her victim, worms dripping from her open mouth.

58:05.760 --> 58:07.200
And she says a line.

58:07.760 --> 58:09.440
And in the movie version, this would be the line

58:09.440 --> 58:12.240
