58:12.960 --> 58:14.080
But instead, she says,

58:15.440 --> 58:17.600
I've seen the future of this country.

58:19.040 --> 58:23.360
And it's going to get so much worse.

58:24.800 --> 58:26.320
The worms don't make her happy.

58:26.320 --> 58:28.320
In fact, they're a kind of contagious misery.

58:29.600 --> 58:32.960
Nobody who is infected ever gets better.

58:33.600 --> 58:38.400
So what can we do about all of the things that we have learned today?

58:38.400 --> 58:40.960
Well, there's actually two questions rolled into one there.

58:40.960 --> 58:43.600
