Well, to be honest,

01:02:18.800 --> 01:02:20.880
there's somebody who does a lot of public education.

01:02:20.880 --> 01:02:21.920
I really hate to admit this,

01:02:21.920 --> 01:02:25.520
but I am not optimistic that education will work.

