Butler says that this movement

01:02:29.040 --> 01:02:32.000
is not only irrational but anti-rational.

01:02:32.000 --> 01:02:34.000
Many of the most prominent people in it

01:02:34.000 --> 01:02:36.080
proudly do not engage

01:02:36.080 --> 01:02:38.320
with any of the academic material on gender.

01:02:39.760 --> 01:02:41.280
At the end of my research journey,

01:02:41.280 --> 01:02:44.080
I realized the reason they don't listen

01:02:44.880 --> 01:02:46.560
is because they feel that listening

01:02:46.560 --> 01:02:47.840
is an act of submission.

01:02:51.280 --> 01:02:55.280
And I can't help it.

01:02:55.280 --> 01:02:56.400
I think that's really sad.

01:02:57.360 --> 01:02:58.560
I really don't want to come across

01:02:58.560 --> 01:03:02.240
as like patronizing or giving people

01:03:02.240 --> 01:03:04.320
with mercy that they wouldn't give me,

01:03:04.320 --> 01:03:06.960
but I think it is really sad

01:03:07.200 --> 01:03:10.400
when people refuse their own complexity,

01:03:10.400 --> 01:03:11.840
when they refuse to become

01:03:12.480 --> 01:03:14.160
the person that they might become

01:03:14.160 --> 01:03:15.200
if they just listened.

01:03:17.200 --> 01:03:20.560
Indeed, there could be no greater enemy

01:03:20.560 --> 01:03:23.920
for philosophy tube than the anti-gender phantasm.

01:03:23.920 --> 01:03:27.360
This show is about compassion and reason

01:03:27.360 --> 01:03:30.480
and sharing knowledge between equals.

01:03:31.680 --> 01:03:33.440
It's born out of my belief that

01:03:34.160 --> 01:03:41.360
thinking and research and words and writing

01:03:43.280 --> 01:03:44.160
that they matter.

01:03:46.400 --> 01:03:48.160
And I'm trans.

01:03:51.440 --> 01:03:53.840
This is my final boss fight.

01:03:55.440 --> 01:03:58.400
Informed public debate becomes impossible

01:03:58.400 --> 01:04:00.320
when some parties refuse to read

01:04:00.320 --> 01:04:02.320
the material under dispute.

01:04:02.400 --> 01:04:04.320
It is nearly impossible to breach

01:04:04.320 --> 01:04:07.120
