01:04:07.120 --> 01:04:08.560
because of the fear that reading

01:04:08.560 --> 01:04:11.760
will introduce confusion into the reader's mind

01:04:11.760 --> 01:04:14.720
or bring her into direct contact with the devil.

01:04:15.360 --> 01:04:17.040
They're skeptical of the academy

01:04:17.040 --> 01:04:19.200
for fear that intellectual debates

01:04:19.200 --> 01:04:22.160
may well confuse them about the values they hold.

01:04:22.880 --> 01:04:25.920
They're refusal to care much about consistency,

01:04:25.920 --> 01:04:28.960
to base their criticisms on a reading of the text,

01:04:28.960 --> 01:04:30.640
their way of snatching phrases

01:04:30.640 --> 01:04:32.240
and making them into lightning rods.

01:04:32.240 --> 01:04:36.880
However, are all finally a refusal to think critically.

